data.description: Motivated Seller!!  $10K towards paint allowance, closing cost or 2-1 buydown with acceptable offer on this steal of a property.  This home is located in a gated community in a much sought after area in SW Arlington.  It boast 5 bds & 2.5 baths with easy access to I-20, Hwys 287 & 820 and only minutes from GP outlet mall, downtown FW, and 25 minutes from downtown Dallas.  It's perfect for a growing or multi-generational family.  The lower level has beautiful laminate wood floors, a huge study, formal dining and breakfast area. The kitchen boast an open concept with plenty of cabinet space, large island that opens to the formal living area.  The primary bedroom comes with a huge walk in closet & bath ensuite with jetted tub, separate shower and double vanity.  Upstairs has the 4 remaining large bedrooms, huge game room for entertaining and laundry area.  The backyard is perfect for cookouts, get togethers and wired for surround sound.  Come make us an offer!
